Date: Wed, 20 Aug 2025 11:18:17 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:hostapd: Refactor advertise TTLM APIs

Refactor the advertised ttlm APIs to re-use later in start ap path.
Bring the number of columns to the limit of 90 characters in ttlm code.
Also changed the ttlm APIs from using memset/memcpy to use wrapper
function os_memcpy/os_memset.

Signed-off-by: Shwetha G K <kshwetha@qti.qualcomm.com>
